> The simplest solution: compctl -/ cd

Um, I think that's not the correct syntax, at least not for
3.0.6:

  # compctl -/ cd
  compctl: bad option: -/

I'll settle for

  compctl -n -g '*(-/) .*(-/) cd pushd

instead. Many thanks

